    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡总统选举前经济增长 4.7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/sri-lanka-economy-expands-4-7-ahead-of-presidential-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡第二季度经济增长速度快于预期，提振了关键选举前的市场人气，而选举可能会影响该国从几十年来最严重的危机中复苏的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/sri-lanka-economy-expands-4-7-ahead-of-presidential-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 10:29:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着当地美元流动性减少，奈拉跌至新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/naira-falls-to-fresh-low-as-local-dollar-liquidity-dwindles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚货币经历了一周的动荡，周四，由于国内外汇市场的美元流动性缩减近一半，尼日利亚货币跌至历史最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/naira-falls-to-fresh-low-as-local-dollar-liquidity-dwindles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 10:16:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿斯利康股价创 14 个月来最差一周表现 因卖出买盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/astrazeneca-shares-set-for-worst-week-in-14-months-on-sell-calls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前英国制药商阿斯利康与合作伙伴第一三共株式会社的实验性肺癌药物发布令人失望的消息，导致两名分析师下调其评级，阿斯利康股价有望创下 2023 年 7 月以来的最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/astrazeneca-shares-set-for-worst-week-in-14-months-on-sell-calls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 10:09:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德暗示欧洲央行可能在 10 月降息，但 12 月更有可能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-officials-stick-with-call-for-gradual-cuts-in-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，如果经济遭遇重大挫折，欧洲央行愿意在 10 月份考虑降息——不过下一轮全面信息要到下次会议上才能公布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-officials-stick-with-call-for-gradual-cuts-in-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 09:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国因恒大欺诈行为对普华永道处以创纪录罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-fines-pwc-halts-business-for-six-months-over-evergrande</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国因普华永道会计师事务所对中国恒大集团的审计存在疏漏，暂停了该事务所的运营六个月，并对其处以创纪录的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-fines-pwc-halts-business-for-six-months-over-evergrande</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 08:17:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元再次上涨 1%，对冲基金加大对日元上涨的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hedge-funds-are-placing-option-bets-for-yen-to-rally-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些对冲基金在期权市场加大对日元走强的押注，因为他们预计日元将延续涨势，日元已成为本季度全球表现最佳的货币 - 周五又上涨了 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hedge-funds-are-placing-option-bets-for-yen-to-rally-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 01:45:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息预期前，黄金连续创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/gold-xauusd-steadies-after-surging-to-record-ahead-of-expected-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元在市场普遍预期美联储下周降息之前延续跌势，金价周四上涨近 2%，创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/gold-xauusd-steadies-after-surging-to-record-ahead-of-expected-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 00:08:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：交易员考虑美联储降息幅度 美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新的美国数据让投资者对美联储下周预期降息幅度产生猜测，导致美国国债价格上涨，美元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 22:17:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡债券持有人与政府举行新一轮谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/sri-lanka-bondholders-hold-new-round-of-talks-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，斯里兰卡私人债权人和该国政府官员本周将举行第三轮会谈，就 126 亿美元违约债券的重组达成一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/sri-lanka-bondholders-hold-new-round-of-talks-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 18:37:18 GMT</pubDate>
